   - Policy-wide modifiers (first-insurance 10%, loyalty -20%, follow-up -15%) apply to policy base premium
   - Processing fee (5 G) added last
   - Rounding in MHPCO's favor: premiums ceil, payouts floor
   - Component block discount: exactly 3 alike components = 60 G instead of 3*25=75 G
   - Claims: 100 G deductible per item, 2x insurance sum cap, special clauses for enchantment>=8 (50%) and dragon material (full)

